      <div><h4>Pacific Palisades + Brentwood</h4><p>Pacific Palisades · Brentwood · Rustic Canyon</p></div>
      <div><h4>Hollywood Hills architectural</h4><p>Hollywood Hills · Laurel Canyon · Outpost Estates</p></div>
